    "A Canadian medical imaging company has developed a technology utilizing retina scans to detect amyloid buildup, a protein associated with Alzheimer's Disease in its early stages (Dangerfield and Katherine, 2023).",
    "As a special instantiation of AI, Large Language Models (LLMs) have been only scarcely explored in the context of dementia care and management.",
